{"completion_tokens": 12240, "generation_max_output_tokens": 2048, "generation_temperature": 1.0, "manifest_path": "/home/li/project/Q-AssertBench/project_code/benchmark_data/tasks/qab20/task.yaml", "model_id": "qwen/qwen3.5-397b-a17b", "prompt_tokens": 469, "prompt_version": "assertion_snippet_v2", "property_type": "oracle_relation", "provider_model_id": "qwen/qwen3.5-397b-a17b", "raw_payload": {"api_base_url": "https://openrouter.ai/api/v1", "completion_tokens": 12240, "finish_reason": "stop", "max_output_tokens": 2048, "model_name": "qwen/qwen3.5-397b-a17b", "prompt_tokens": 469, "provider_type": "openai-compatible", "response_id": "gen-1775044273-L2drPPawysbDegjnPSiJ", "response_model": "qwen/qwen3.5-397b-a17b-20260216", "task_id": "QAB20", "temperature": 1.0, "total_tokens": 12709, "trial_index": 20}, "raw_response": "```python\nassert len(counts) > 0, \"No counts observed\"\nfor key in counts:\n    # Qiskit bitstrings are MSB left: c3 c2 c1 c0\n    # Qubits: 3(out1), 2(out0), 1(in1), 0(in0)\n    # Input bits are at indices 2 and 3 (q1, q0)\n    # Output bits are at indices 0 and 1 (q3, q2)\n    assert len(key) == 4, \"Expected 4-bit keys\"\n    inp = key[2:]\n    out = key[:2]\n    # Hidden period is 11 (binary), flip both input bits\n    inp_val = int(inp, 2)\n    inp_pair_val = inp_val ^ 0b11\n    inp_pair = format(inp_pair_val, '02b')\n    partner = out + inp_pair\n    assert partner in counts, f\"Period pair {partner} for {key} missing\"\n```", "task_family": "algorithmic_semantics", "task_id": "QAB20", "total_tokens": 12709, "trial_index": 20}
